Subject: HTTP Error 500.31 - Failed to load ASP.NET Core runtime
Description: Hello, I have updated PingCastle to the latest version, but after running it, I received an error. I have downloaded and installed the latest version of ASP.NET, but I still could not open the page and access the settings to configure it.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c: copy paste the update files in the pingcastle directory
What_We_Know__c:
Customer getting errors after upgrading ASP.NET. As I can see in the screenshot, he installed v9. 
PingCastle supports v8.xx
Next_Steps__c:
Wait for customer to install ASP.NET 8.xx
updated ASP.NET to 8.XX
uninstalled previous versions
turned on logging
modified webconfig file
Solution_Comment__c: after modifying webconfig file and updating ASP.NET PingCastlePro works as expected
